        "text_nycXyP": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Urinefree</strong> is a versatile solution that can be applied wherever it's needed—whether in toilets, urinals, or even in laundry to remove urine stains. It’s also highly effective at eliminating stale alcohol odors from wooden bar counters, removing vomit smells and stains, and treating carpets, upholstery, and more.</p><p>Where urine is present, our powerful <strong>bio-enzymatic formula</strong> works by breaking down the uric acid crystals at the source.</p><p>When applied correctly, it eliminates both the odor and the stain—leaving your facility clean, hygienic, and fresh.</p><p>Urinals are a common source of odor. Environmental Biotech’s <strong>Flow Fresh®</strong> system, available in screen, gel, or drip formats, targets the issue directly—eliminating odors and keeping plumbing lines clear. <strong>No more urinal drain blockages!</strong></p><p>Visit <a>www.urinefree.com</a> to learn more.</p><p>We also offer a complete program for traditional and waterless urinals—a <strong>cost-effective solution</strong> to a long-standing problem. Try it and experience the results yourself.</p><p>The program is proven effective in restrooms, nursing homes, schools, bedding, clothing, furniture, pet training areas, pet accidents, carpet stains—even vomit and blood cleanup.</p><p><strong>Seeing is believing</strong> when it comes to the true power of bioremediation!</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
